3. cs.SD (Speech and Audio Processing): The paper specifically deals with reconstructing phases from amplitude spectrograms of speeches, which falls under the domain of speech and audio processing. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a deep neural network architecture for phase reconstruction, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
5. cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper deals with speech processing, which is a sub-domain of natural language processing, falling under the domain of computation and language.
